Asset conversion Important tips, please read carefully Due to the upgrade of the main network of uyt network, asset conversion is required before withdrawal. 
The process is as follows The first step 1、Fill in the withdrawal amount and click the asset conversion button. 2、The main network carries out asset conversion according to the current currency asset quantity. Asset conversion needs to wait 24 hours The second step 1、View the list to be withdrawn and click the details of the currency to be withdrawn. 2、Fill in the withdrawal address and remarks,Click the withdraw button. 3、Check address, withdraw money quantity and input password. This process needs to wait for about 3 blocks to confirm
